\id 1PE 1 Peter in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08 
\h 1 Piɛɛ 
\toc1 Piɛɛ lá sɛ̃́ia 
\toc2 1 Piɛɛ 
\toc3 1Piɛ 
\mt1 PIƐƐ LÁ SƐ̃IA 
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ 
\ip Piɛɛ láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ za Loma Yesude pↄ́ aa fãaaa wà tà bùsu pↄ́ wì mɛ tia Tuukii bùsuuↄnɛɛ. Gãli pↄ́ aa ku a guuↄ dɛ gãli pↄ́ Pↄlu ń aà ìwaↄ dàalɛdaalɛↄ ũ. Yↄ̃a pãsĩ ń lé an Yesudekɛ yã́i, ↄ̃ wàlɛ ĩadamá. Piɛɛ tò an laai tà Yesu Kilisiwa, à mɛ̀ an baa ku Kilisi taasikɛa guu. 
\ip Fↄkpaama ń Lua sáaukpaao gbɛa, Piɛɛ lá Lua ń suabà dↄ̀ńgu, ↄ̃ aa tãmaa pↄ́ lí ń nɛo vĩ Yesu Kilisi gaa ń aà vuao sabai (1.3-12). À ń gbá laai aaↄ itɛ̃kɛ, aa tó ń kua aↄ adoa naa Yesu Kilisiwa (1.13-2.10). À Yesu ↄlɛsɛ̀ à yãdàonɛ́ à mɛ̀ à kũ̀ aaↄ náai vĩ ń yãkɛaↄ guu, atɛ̃sa kua yↄ̃a guu. À lɛdàmá an kua dṹnia guu, à mɛ̀ aa misiilɛ gbãadeↄnɛ, zĩkɛnaↄ misiilɛ ń diiↄnɛ, nↄɛↄ misiilɛ ń zã́ↄnɛ, Yesudeↄ píi iↄ yekↄ̃zi (2.11-4.19). Lɛɛ 5 guu à lɛdà Yesude gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄwa ń ɛ̀waasoↄ ń luanaaikɛnaↄ píi, à mɛ̀ aa zɛ gbãa kua yã'ĩa guu, aa Lua lɛgbɛ̃anɛ́ papaa dã́. Lápi làa ń fↄkpaamáo. 
\ip À kũ̀ láɛ bee kyokɛnaↄ wɛtã luanaaikɛa guu, baa tó aalɛ taasi kpeletaa bui kɛ, kɛ́ an kua e Lua tↄbↄ, i zɛ'ↄlↄ Yesusaideↄnɛ yã́i. Tó luanaaikɛnsaiↄ yãmaa pↄ́ aalɛ kɛↄ è, aa Lua sáaukpa yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩ (2.12). 
\c 1  
\s1 Tãmaa pↄ́ lí ń nɛ́o 
\p  
\v 1 Mámɛmaa Yesu Kilisi zĩna Piɛɛ, mámɛ ma láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ Lua gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa dɛ nibↄↄ ũ dṹniaɛ bee guu aa fãaaa bùsuɛ beeuↄnɛ: Pↄ̃ntu, Galati, Kapadosi, Azi ń Bitinio.  
\v 2 Mae Lua dↄ̀aa á dↄ̃, ↄ̃ à á sɛ́, a gↄ̃ aà pↄ́ ũ ń aà Nisĩna gbãao, kɛ́ à misiilɛ Yesu Kilisiɛ, aà au i á gbãsĩ wolo.\f + \fr 1.2 \ft Lev 17.11, Ɛbɛ 9.22\f* Lua gbɛ̃kɛ ń aafiao kã́fĩɛ́. 
\p  
\v 3 Wà Lua wá Dii Yesu Kilisi Mae sáaukpa! Aà sùuu zↄ̃ↄ guu à wá í dafu ń Yesu Kilisi fɛlɛ bↄa gau gbãao, ↄ̃ wá tãmaa pↄ́ lí ń nɛ́o vĩ,  
\v 4 asa gba pↄ́ dilɛaɛ́ luabɛpi lí ↄ̃̀ↄkpao, ìli gbãsĩkpao, a maa lí láao.  
\v 5 Lua sↄu mà à á suaba a náai pↄ́ álɛ kɛ yã́i, ↄ̃ àlɛ á dↄ̃́a ń a gbãao e à gɛ bↄò gↄↄgbɛzãzĩ.  
\v 6 Álɛ pↄnakɛ ń yã́pio, baa kɛ́ álɛ taasikɛ gĩa yↄↄ yã'ĩa bui dasi yã́i.  
\v 7 Lá wì vua maa dↄ̃ tɛ́ guu, màa yã'ĩapiↄ lɛ́ á luanaaikɛa yↄ̃, asa á luanaaikɛapi bɛɛɛ vĩ dɛ vua pↄ́ a gawi ì láaa maamaaɛ. Tó a bↄ maa, Lua a á sáaukpa Yesu Kilisi mↄgↄↄzĩ, a á kpɛla ń gawio.  
\v 8 Baa kɛ́ i aà eo, á yeaàzi. Baa kɛ́ i wɛsiaàlɛ gĩao,\f + \fr 1.8 \ft Zãa 20.29\f* álɛ aà náaikɛ, ↄ̃ álɛ pↄna zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ gɛ̃̀ oaa kɛ,  
\v 9 kɛ́ álɛ á luanaaikɛa gbɛ'e á suabaa ũ yã́i. 
\p  
\v 10 Ãnabiↄ dↄ̀aa gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua a kɛɛ́ yã'ò, aa suabaapi yã́ gwà aa a tàasikà.  
\v 11 Kilisi Nisĩna kú ń guu, à dↄ̀aa taasi pↄ́ Kilisipi a kɛ ònɛ́ ń gawi pↄ́ a e a gbɛao, ↄ̃ aa wɛ̀ɛlɛ wà yã́pi zɛ́ dↄ̃ ń a kɛgↄↄo.\f + \fr 1.11 \ft Luk 24.25-26\f* 
\v 12 Ɔ̃ Lua tò aa dↄ̃̀ kɛ́ yã́ pↄ́ aalɛ opi dɛ ń gↄↄ pↄ́ ũo, á pↄ́ɛ. Tiasa baonakpanaↄ yã́pi òɛ́ ń Lua Nisĩna pↄ́ Luapi aà zĩ̀ à bↄ̀ luabɛ gbãao. Baa malaikaↄ ì dɛ̃ɛka yã́pi dↄ̃ai. 
\s1 Wá kua àↄ adoa 
\p  
\v 13 Ayãmɛto à á làasoo vu iu, íↄ ázĩa kũa dↄ̃, á wɛ́ iↄ dↄ gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua a kɛɛ́ Yesu Kilisi mↄgↄↄzĩzi seasai.  
\v 14 Lá á dɛ Lua Nɛ́ pↄ́ lɛ́ aà yãmaↄ ũ, ásu to dↄ́ɛ'ĩi pↄ́ á vĩ yãa á wɛ́siagↄↄ dↄaaɛ́o.  
\v 15 Lua kua adoaɛ. Lá à á sisi à á sɛ́, á kua líↄ adoa á yãkɛa píi guu màa sↄ̃.  
\v 16 Asa a kɛ̃a láu wà mɛ̀: 
\q1 Á kua líↄ adoa, 
\q1 asa ma kua adoaɛ.\f + \fr 1.16 \ft Lev 19.2\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Lá Lua ì yã́kpalɛkɛ ń baadeo a yãkɛawa ń wɛgwasai, tó álɛ aà sisi Mae, à vĩakɛɛ̀ á nibↄkɛ guu la.  
\v 18 Á dↄ̃ lá Lua á bↄ́ kua gii pↄ́ dɛ á fɛlɛkaa ũ guu. Lua i á bo ń pↄ́ pↄ́ a gawi ì láao no, vua ge ã́nusu,  
\v 19 à á bó ń Kilisi pↄ́ dɛ sã sãasai gbãsĩsai ũ au gawideoɛ.\f + \fr 1.19 \ft Zãa 1.29, Ɛbɛ 9.14\f* 
\v 20 Lua dↄ̀aa aà dìlɛ zadↄ̃ i dṹnia kálɛo, ↄ̃ à bↄ̀ɛ́aànↄ gupuau gↄↄ gbɛzãɛ beeↄzĩ.  
\v 21 Aà yã́ musu ↄ̃ álɛ Lua náaikɛ. Lua aà bↄ̀ gau à gawi kpàwà, kɛ́ à e a náaikɛ, á wɛ́ iↄ dↄazi. 
\p  
\v 22 Lá misiilɛa sĩanaɛ á gbãsĩ wòlo, ↄ̃ á gbɛ̃kɛ vĩ ń kↄ̃o mↄafilisai, àↄ yekↄ̃i ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo.  
\v 23 Lua á í dafu ń a yã́ wɛ̃nide pↄ́ ìↄ ku gbãaoɛ. Yã́pi dɛ pↄbui pↄ́ ì ga ũo, pↄbui pↄ́ lí gaoɛ. 
\q1  
\v 24 Gbɛ̃́pii dɛ lán sɛ̃waɛ, 
\q1 an gawi píi dɛ lán sɛ̃vuwaɛ. 
\q1 Sɛ̃ ì gaga, a vú ì kwɛ́, 
\q1  
\v 25 ãma Dii yã́ ìↄ ku gↄↄpiiɛ.\f + \fr 1.25 \ft Isa 40.6-8\f* 
\m Yã́pi mɛ́ dɛ baona pↄ́ wa kpàɛ́ ũ. 
\c 2  
\s1 Gbɛ̀ wɛ̃nide 
\p  
\v 1 Ayãmɛto à yãvãi píi tó ń ɛɛ píio ń mↄafilio ń wɛdↄakↄ̃ɛo ń kↄ̃yaaao.  
\v 2 Lá nɛ́tɛ̃naↄ ìↄ yↄ̃́'i nidɛ, àↄ Lua yã́ pↄ́ dɛ lán vĩ'ipu wásawasawa nidɛ màa sↄ̃, kɛ́ à e gbã á suabaa guu,  
\v 3 asa á dↄ̃̀ sa kɛ́ Dii maa.\f + \fr 2.3 \ft Soũ 34.9\f* 
\v 4 À sↄ̃aàzi, Gbɛ̀ wɛ̃nide pↄ́ wà pãkpài, Lua aà sɛ̀ bɛɛɛde ũ.  
\v 5 Ápiↄ sↄ̃ ámɛ á gbɛ̀ wɛ̃nide pↄ́ Lua lɛ́ a kpɛ́ ɛ̃booↄ ũ. Ámɛ á aà gbàgbanaↄ ũ, i sa pↄ́ ì kaaàgu o ń aà Nisĩna gbãao Yesu Kilisi sabai.  
\v 6 Asa a kɛ̃a Luayãtaalau wà mɛ̀: 
\q1 Gwa, málɛ gbɛ dilɛ Siↄna, 
\q1 ɛ̃daalɛgbɛ bɛɛɛde pↄ́ má sɛ̀ ũ. 
\q1 Wí a gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ aà náaikɛ kũo.\f + \fr 2.6 \ft Isa 28.16\f* 
\m  
\v 7 A dɛ gbɛ̀ bɛɛɛde ũ á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ álɛ aà náaikɛↄnɛ, ãma a dɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ aà náaikɛoↄnɛ màao. 
\q1 Gbɛ pↄ́ ɛ̃bonaↄ pãkpài 
\q1 mɛ́ gↄ̃̀ gbɛↄ mide ũ.\f + \fr 2.7 \ft Soũ 118.22\f* 
\m  
\v 8 Màa lↄ a dɛ: 
\q1 Gbɛ pↄ́ wì gɛ̃mbↄlɛwà ũ, 
\q1 gbɛsi pↄ́ aaì kpaa aa fu ũ.\f + \fr 2.8 \ft Isa 8.14-15\f* 
\m Aa gɛ̃mbↄlɛwà kɛ́ aai Lua yãdao yã́i. Beewa Lua dìlɛnɛ́. 
\p  
\v 9 Ámɛ á bui pↄ́ Lua ń sɛ́ↄ ũ, kíaↄ ũ, aà gbàgbanaↄ ũ,\f + \fr 2.9 \ft Bↄa 19.5-6\f* gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ an kua adoaↄ ũ, aà gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ ũ, kɛ́ à Lua pↄ́ á sisi a bↄ gusiau, à gɛ̃̀ánↄ a gupua bↄnsaɛde guu táasilɛ.\f + \fr 2.9 \ft Isa 9.1-2\f* 
\q1  
\v 10 Á dɛ Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ ũ yãao, 
\q1 tiasa ↄ̃ a gↄ̃ a ũ.\f + \fr 2.10 \ft Lom 9.25-26\f* 
\q1 Lua i sùuukɛánↄ yãao, 
\q1 tiasa ↄ̃ a kɛ̀ánↄ.\f + \fr 2.10 \ft Oze 2.25\f* 
\s1 Kua luanaaikɛnsaiↄ guu 
\p  
\v 11 Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, lá á dɛ nibↄ bↄ̀mↄↄ ũ la, málɛ lɛdawáɛ, à mikɛ̃ á dↄ́ɛ'ĩi pↄ́ aaì zĩkaánↄↄwa.  
\v 12 Àↄ ku gbɛ̃́ bɛɛɛdeↄ ũ luanaaikɛnsaiↄ guu. Beewa baa tó aalɛ á dilɛ vãikɛnaↄ ũ, tó aa yãmaa pↄ́ álɛ kɛↄ è, aa Lua sáaukpa yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩ. 
\p  
\v 13 À misiilɛ iko pↄ́ gbɛ̃nazĩna dìlɛɛ píi Dii yã́i, kía pↄ́ iko vĩ dɛńlan nò,  
\v 14 gbãade pↄ́ a dìlɛ aà vãikɛnaↄ wɛtã aà maakɛnaↄ sáaukpan nò.\f + \fr 2.14 \ft Lom 13.1-5\f* 
\v 15 Lua pↄeãn kɛ: À yãmaakɛ à lɛsↄkpa sↄũ wɛ́siadeↄnɛ.  
\v 16 A gↄ̃ wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũɛ, ãma ásu tó á gↄ̃a wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ gↄ̃ɛ́ vãikɛa zɛ́ ũo. Àↄ ku Lua zↄ̀blenaↄ ũ.  
\v 17 À gbɛ̃́pii kpɛla. Àↄ ye á Yesude deeↄzi. À vĩakɛ Luaɛ. À kía kpɛla. 
\p  
\v 18 Zĩkɛnaↄ, à misiilɛ á diiↄnɛ, í zↄ̃ↄkɛ dↄ̃nɛ́ yã́pii guu. I kɛ dii maa nↄ̀sɛdoũdeↄ ńtɛ̃ɛ no, ń a pãsĩↄɛ lↄ.  
\v 19 Tó wà ĩadàwá pã, tó a mɛnakɛ̀ò Lua yã́i, bee ài vĩɛ́.  
\v 20 Tó wà á gbɛ̃́ á tàae yã́i, tó a mɛnakɛ̀ò, bee tↄ́ vĩ má ni? Ãma tó a taasikɛ̀ yãmaa pↄ́ á kɛ yã́i, tó a mɛnakɛ̀ò, Lua a á sáaukpa.  
\v 21 Bee yã́i Lua á sisii à á sɛ́. Kilisi taasikɛ̀ɛ́ à zɛ'ↄ̀lↄɛ́, kɛ́ àↄ tɛ a iai yã́iɛ. 
\q1  
\v 22 I duunakɛo, 
\q1 wi ma à ɛɛtòo.\f + \fr 2.22 \ft Isa 53.9\f* 
\m  
\v 23 Kɛ́ wà aà sↄ̃̀sↄ̃, i a zã́simáo. Kɛ́ à taasikɛ̀, i yãpãsĩ onɛ́o, à zɛ̀ ń Lua yã́kpalɛkɛn maaoɛ.  
\v 24 Ɔ̃mɛ wá duuna dì a miwa\f + \fr 2.24 \ft Isa 53.11-12\f* à gàò líwa, kɛ́ wá bàa su àↄ kú ń duunao lↄo, wíↄ ku maakɛa guu. Aà flàala iaↄ mɛ́ wá gbãgbã.\f + \fr 2.24 \ft Isa 53.5\f* 
\v 25 Asa a sãsã lán sãↄwa yãaɛ,\f + \fr 2.25 \ft Isa 53.6\f* ↄ̃ a ɛa su á Dãna ń á Dↄ̃̀anaowa tiasa. 
\c 3  
\s1 Kua ń kↄ̃o 
\p  
\v 1 Nↄɛↄ sↄ̃, à misiilɛ á zã́ↄnɛ.\f + \fr 3.1 \ft Ɛfɛ 5.22, Kls 3.18\f* Tó an gbɛ̃eↄ lɛ́ Lua yãdao, á kua a ń lilɛ. Baa tó i yãe onɛ́o,  
\v 2 aa e á kú gbãsĩsai mɛ́ álɛ misiilɛnɛ́.  
\v 3 Á kɛfɛnkɛ wɛɛlɛa su àↄ dɛ mɛkaa yã́ ũo, mitãa ge nↄamblebↄↄ ge pↄkasadaan nò.\f + \fr 3.3 \ft 1Tim 2.9\f* 
\v 4 Aàↄ dɛ á nↄ̀sɛ guu yã́ pↄ́ lí láao ũ, nↄ̀sɛniɛ ń zĩabusaao. Bee mɛ́ gbia Luaɛ.  
\v 5 Asa beewa nↄɛ lousisina pↄ́ an wɛ́ dↄ Luazi yãaↄ ńzĩa kɛ̀kɛ, aa misìilɛ ń zã́ↄnɛ.  
\v 6 Màa Sala dɛ, ì Ablahaũ yãma ì oɛ̀ Baa.\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Daa 18.12\f* Tó álɛ yãmaakɛ, mɛ́ álɛ pↄ́ pↄ́ wì vĩakɛɛ̀ yãdao, a Sala ↄlɛsɛ̀n we.  
\v 7 Màa gↄ̃ɛↄ sↄ̃ àↄ kúńnↄ nↄɛkɛdↄ̃anɛ́ guu,\f + \fr 3.7 \ft Ɛfɛ 5.25, Kls 3.19\f* íli yãmamá, kɛ́ pↄe su kpáɛ́ á wabikɛa guuo, asa á dɛ wɛ̃ni gbablenaↄ ũ sãnuɛ. 
\p  
\v 8 Bee gbɛa àↄ lɛdoũ vĩ ń kↄ̃o ápii. Àↄ wɛ̃nadↄ̃kↄ̃ɛ, àↄ yekↄ̃i, àↄ gbɛ̃kɛ vĩ ń kↄ̃o, í busakↄ̃ɛ.  
\v 9 Ásuli vãi fĩabo ń vãioo. Ásuli gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ á sↄ̃sↄ̃ sↄ̃́sↄ̃o. À samaa'oɛ̀, asa Lua á sisi à báaadaágu yã́iɛ.\f + \fr 3.9 \ft Lom 12.14, 17\f* 
\q1  
\v 10 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ye a wɛ̃ni àↄ maa, 
\q1 mɛ́ a ye a kua àↄ na, 
\q1 aà a lɛ́ fↄ̃ ń yãvãi oao, 
\q1 asuli to ɛɛ bↄ a lɛ́uo. 
\q1  
\v 11 Aà mikɛ̃ vãiwa, i maakɛ, 
\q1 aà aafia zɛ́ wɛɛlɛ, iↄ tɛi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Asa Dii ì wɛ́tɛ gbɛ̃maaↄzi, 
\q1 ì swã́kpa an wabikɛaↄzi. 
\q1 Dii ì mikpɛdↄ vãikɛnaↄnɛ.\f + \fr 3.12 \ft Soũ 34.13-17\f* 
\s1 Taasikɛa maakɛa yã́i 
\p  
\v 13 Tó á ãiavĩ ń maakɛao, démɛ a á wɛtãi?  
\v 14 Baa tó a su taasikɛ̀ maakɛa yã́i, báaadeↄn á ũ.\f + \fr 3.14 \ft Mat 5.10\f* Ásuli vĩakɛ an wɛ́tɛ̃aɛo, ásu sↄ̃̀deedeekɛo.  
\v 15 À Kilisi dↄ̃ Dii ũ á sↄ̃ guu.\f + \fr 3.15 \ft Isa 8.12-13\f* Àↄ ku sↄu guu gↄↄpii, kɛ́ à e yãwe gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ á la yã́ pↄ́ á wɛ́ dↄi miiwa.  
\v 16 Àli onɛ́ busɛbusɛ ń bɛɛɛ dↄ̃anɛ́o. À onɛ́ ń nↄ̀sɛpuao lↄ, kɛ́ wí e gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ á sↄ̃sↄ̃ maa pↄ́ álɛ kɛ á Yesudekɛ yã́iↄ kṹ.  
\v 17 Taasikɛa lá Lua yeiwa maakɛa yã́i maa dɛ taasikɛa yãvãikɛa yã́ila. 
\p  
\v 18 Kilisi gà gɛ̃n do duunawoloa yã́iɛ. Tàaesaide gà wá tàaedeↄ yã́i, kɛ́ à e gɛ́wanↄ Lua kĩ́i. Wà aà dɛ̀ aà gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guu, ↄ̃ Lua aà vù aà nisĩnkɛ guu.  
\v 19 Aà nisĩnkɛpi guu à gɛ̀ waasokɛ̀ nisĩna pↄ́ wà ń ká kpɛ́uↄnɛ.\f + \fr 3.19 \ft 1Piɛ 4.6\f* 
\v 20 Aa bↄ̀ Lua yã́ kpɛ yãaɛ, gↄↄ pↄ́ àlɛ mɛnakɛ e Nↄee gɛ̀ a gó'ilɛna kɛ làaò. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ bↄ̀ íu aafia gópi sabaiↄ dasio, gbɛ̃ↄn swaaↄ̃ɛ.\f + \fr 3.20 \ft Daa 7.7\f* 
\v 21 Ípi mɛ́ dɛ á da'ilɛkɛa pↄ́ ì á suaba taa ũ tia. Da'ilɛkɛapiá mɛ̀ gbãsĩwoloa yã́ no. Lɛgbɛ̃a Luaɛ ń nↄ̀sɛpuaoɛ. Ì á suaba kɛ́ Yesu Kilisi bↄ̀ gau yã́i.  
\v 22 À ikokɛ̀ malaikaↄ ń tã́aↄ ń ń gbãadeↄ ń ń ikodeↄwa, ↄ̃ à tà luabɛ, a ku aà ↄplaai. 
\c 4  
\s1 Kua Lua pↄ́ ũ 
\p  
\v 1 Lá Kilisi gà a gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guu, ápiↄ à bee nↄ̀sɛ da sↄ̃, asa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gà a gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ yã́ musu kɛ̃̀ duunawaɛ.  
\v 2 Gↄↄ pↄ́ gↄ̃̀ɛ́ á kua guu, á dↄ́ɛ'ĩi suli dↄaaɛ́ lↄo, sema Lua pↄeã.  
\v 3 Á kua luayãdansaiↄ yãkɛa guu yãa mↄ̀ lɛ. Á kú yãa wisaiyãkɛa guu ń dↄ́ɛ'ĩio ń wɛ̃dɛkɛao ń lalasi kↄ̃̀ↄo ń wɛ̃mi wɛ̃zĩgbaao ń tã́agbagbaao, pↄ́ Lua ye a gĩyãio.  
\v 4 Lá ili sińnↄ an lalasi zↄ̃ↄpi kɛa guu lↄo, ì kɛnɛ́ yãbↄnsaɛ ũ, aaì á tↄbɛ̃ɛsi.  
\v 5 Aa ń yãkɛaↄ dau siu Luaɛ. Aà yã́kpalɛkɛa ń gbɛ̃́ bɛ̃́ɛↄ ń gyaadeↄ sↄu mà.  
\v 6 Wà baonakpà gyaadepiↄnɛ lↄ, kɛ́ an gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ yã́ zↄ̃̀lɛmá an gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guu lán gbɛ̃́piiwaↄ e aaↄ ku nisĩnkɛ guu lán Luawa.\f + \fr 4.6 \ft 1Piɛ 3.18\f* 
\p  
\v 7 Pↄ́pii láaa kà kãi. Ayãmɛto àↄ dɛ laaideↄ ũ, íↄ ázĩa kũa dↄ̃, kɛ́ àↄ wabikɛ Luawa yã́i.  
\v 8 Yã́ pↄ́ dɛ a píia, àↄ yekↄ̃i ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo, asa yea gbɛ̃́i ì láka tàaea dasi.\f + \fr 4.8 \ft Yaa 10.12\f* 
\v 9 À kↄ̃ yàaekɛ yã́kũtɛ̃kasai.  
\v 10 Lá Lua gbadà á baadeɛ, à dↄkↄ̃lɛ ń gbapiↄ Lua báaa bui dodo ziia maaↄ ũ.  
\v 11 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ waasokɛna ũ, aà Lua yã'onɛ́. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ dↄnlɛde ũ, aà dↄńlɛ ń gbãa pↄ́ Lua a gbao,\f + \fr 4.11 \ft Lom 12.6-7\f* kɛ́ à Lua tↄbↄ yã́pii guu ń Yesu Kilisi gbãao. Ɔ̃mɛ gawi vĩ ń gbãao gↄↄpii! Ãmi. 
\s1 Taasikɛa Yesudekɛ yã́i 
\p  
\v 12 Ma gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ, ásu to yↄ̃a pãsĩ pↄ́ lɛ́ á le bↄ á saɛ lándↄ̃ yã́kanla mɛ́ á léwao.  
\v 13 Lá á baa ku Kilisi taasikɛa guu, à pↄnakɛò, kɛ́ à e àↄ pↄna zↄ̃ↄ vĩ gↄↄ pↄ́ Kilisipi a bↄ gupuau ń gawio.  
\v 14 Tó wà á sↄ̃sↄ̃ Kilisi tↄ́ pↄ́ kúwá yã́i, báaadeↄn á ũ, asa Lua Nisĩna gawide diaɛ́ɛ.  
\v 15 Á gbɛ̃e su taasikɛ gbɛ̃dɛa ge kpã́i'oa ge vãikɛa ge gudɛ yã́io.  
\v 16 Tó a taasikɛ̀ á Kilisidekɛ yã́i, asu kɛɛ́ wíyã ũo. À Lua sáaukpa kɛ́ Yesu tↄ́ kúwá yã́i.  
\v 17 Asa ĩadaama pìla, Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ ↄ̃ à dàalɛmá. Lá wámɛ à dàalɛwá sɛ̃́ia, a midɛ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ gì baona pↄ́ bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i síiↄ kpelewa ni? 
\q1  
\v 18 Tó gbɛ̃maaↄ suabaa zĩ'ũ, 
\q1 a bↄ ń duunde luayãdansaiↄ kpelewa ni?\f + \fr 4.18 \ft Yaa 11.31\f* 
\m  
\v 19 Ayãmɛto gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ taasikɛ Lua pↄeãkɛa yã́iↄ aa ńzĩa na ń Kɛna náaideɛ a ↄzĩ, aai wɛtã wàↄ maakɛ. 
\c 5  
\s1 Lua sã kpàsa gwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Málɛ lɛda á gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄwa sa. Gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄn ma ũ sↄ̃. Má dɛ taasi pↄ́ Kilisi kɛ̀ seelade ũ, mɛ́ ma bàa kú ń gawi pↄ́ a bↄ gupuauo sↄ̃.  
\v 2 Àↄ dɛ kpàsa pↄ́ Lua kàlɛɛ́ dãnaↄ ũ.\f + \fr 5.2 \ft Zãa 21.15-17\f* À ↄliai ń pↄeão teasisai lá Lua yeiwa. I kɛ ↄ̃awɛɛlɛa yã́i no. À kɛ ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo.  
\v 3 Ásuli gbãable gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wa nàɛ́ á ↄzĩpiↄwao. À tó á kua á sãↄ dazɛwa,  
\v 4 í kíafua pↄ́ a gawi lí láao e gↄↄ pↄ́ Sãdãnki mↄ̀. 
\p  
\v 5 Á ɛ̀waasoↄ sↄ̃, à misiilɛ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄnɛ. Ápii à ázĩa busakↄ̃ɛ, í dↄkↄ̃lɛ, asa: 
\q1 Lua ì íbɛlɛsɛ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì azĩa sɛ lɛsĩo, 
\q1 mɛ́ a gbɛ̃kɛ vĩ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì azĩa busao.\f + \fr 5.5 \ft Yaa 3.34\f* 
\m  
\v 6 Ayãmɛto à ázĩa busa Lua gbãadeɛ, i á kã́fĩ gↄↄ pↄ́ a dìlɛwa.\f + \fr 5.6 \ft Mat 23.12\f* 
\v 7 À ↄzↄ̃ɛ̀ á yã'ↄ̃mai píi, asa ì laaidↄwá.\f + \fr 5.7 \ft Soũ 55.23\f* 
\p  
\v 8 À itɛ̃kɛ àↄ kú ń laaio. Á ibɛɛ Ibiisi dɛ lán nↄ̀ↄmusu pↄ́ lɛ́ ↄ́ↄlↄwaɛ. Àlɛ kpálɛkɛázi, àlɛ gbɛ̃́ wɛɛlɛ kṹ.  
\v 9 À giɛ̀, í zɛ gbãa luanaaikɛa guu, asa á dↄ̃ kɛ́ á Yesude dee pↄ́ kú dṹnia guuↄ píi lɛ́ taasi doũpi kɛɛ.  
\v 10 Lua Báaapiide á sisi a gawi pↄ́ lí láaowa naa Kilisiwaɛ. Tó a taasikɛ̀ yↄↄ, a á bↄ maa, i á zɛ gíũgiũ, i á gba gbãa, i á zɛdↄ.  
\v 11 Ɔ̃mɛ gbãa vĩ gↄↄpii! Ãmi. 
\p  
\v 12 Wá gbɛ̃do Silivɛ̃ɛ\f + \fr 5.12 \ft Zĩn 15.22\f* pↄ́ má aà dↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ náaide ũ mɛ́ lá yↄↄnaɛ bee kɛ̃̀ɛ́mɛɛ. Ma lɛdàowá, mɛ́ má dɛ a seelade ũ kɛ́ yã́ pↄ́ má ò dɛ Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛanɛ́ sĩana ũɛ. À zɛò gíũgiũ.  
\v 13 Babɛli\f + \fr 5.13 \ft Zia 17.5, 18\f* gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua ń sɛ́ lááwaↄ fↄkpàwá. Ma nɛ́ Maaku fↄkpàwá lↄ.  
\v 14 À fↄkpakↄ̃wa ń lɛ́pɛakↄ̃wao yeakↄ̃i guu.\f + \fr 5.14 \ft Lom 16.16\f* Lua á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ á naa Kilisiwaↄ gba aafia ápii.